Lunarpine flew his transport pod north, his scans showed two battles 
going obn. one at the CF and one at the Pred Cave. he fealt he should 
help one or the other out but knew that nobody else was planning on 
checking out the new arrivals. He was a recon bot, his function was 
to be the first into possibly hazardous situations. Besides the 
battles meant the predacons wouldn't have time to worry about one 
unarmed transport pod. Lunarpine kept his scanners on full. he didn't 
want any nasty surprises from the other predacon base.
